The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Steven Dosztan, Appellant.

Order affirmed. All concur. (Appeal from an order of Lewis Special Term denying petitioner’s application to vacate a judgment convicting him of the crime of burglary, third degree.) Present — McCurn, P. J., Vaughan, Kimball, Williams and Bastow, JJ.
